[[!meta title="ctt 0.8 released"]]

## Introduction

[[ctt|software/ctt]] is a time tracking tool for geeks. 
It supports project based reporting, custom report formats and 
stores its data in a [[cconfig|docs/cconfig]] database.

## Changes

    * Added -e / --regexp support for filtering entries on report
    * Added -i / --ignore-case support
    * Renamed -s/-e to --sd / --ed (to allow -e for expression)


